1
00:00:06,999 --> 00:00:08,479
Danny呢?
Where's Danny?

2
00:00:08,559 --> 00:00:11,029
不知道 上飞机后 就再没见过他
I don't know.He disappeared just after we took off.

3
00:00:11,119 --> 00:00:12,519
他在那儿!
Here he is.

4
00:00:20,599 --> 00:00:22,789
好的 今天过得很开心
Right,listen,it's been fun,hasn't it?

5
00:00:22,879 --> 00:00:25,789
我会给你们打电话的 我保证过
All right and I'm going to call you just like I promised I said I would.

6
00:00:25,879 --> 00:00:27,469
你的头怎么样了?
How's your head?

7
00:00:27,559 --> 00:00:29,629
没大碍 我会告诉技术部
That's all right,I'll call engineering.I'll get that soap dispenser...

8
00:00:29,719 --> 00:00:33,189
叫他们把给皂机弄低点 太危险了 可能会弄伤眼睛
moved down a little bit.It's dangerous,could have your eye out.

9
00:00:33,279 --> 00:00:35,749
好了 该走了 亲一个!
Okay,got to go.Big kiss.

10
00:00:36,959 --> 00:00:38,679
很好 走吧!
There it is,go on.

11
00:00:48,639 --> 00:00:52,029
- 看够了没? - 哦 让我有点触景生情
- Finished? - Yeah,just having a flashback.

12
00:00:53,199 --> 00:00:55,429
- Ash 弄辆车来 - 没问题
-Ash,get us a car. - Right.

13
00:00:56,439 --> 00:00:58,269
那就是你消失的原因?
So that's where you disappeared to?

14
00:00:58,359 --> 00:01:01,749
空姐们有点小麻烦 鸡毛蒜皮的小事而已
Well,there's something about trolley dollies.It must be all that makeup.

15
00:01:01,839 --> 00:01:04,669
- 花了3个小时? - 哦 没有
- Three hours? - Oh,no.

16
00:01:05,439 --> 00:01:08,029
后两个小时 我在驾驶飞机
No,the last two,I was flying the plane.

